ey have not heard of or have not thought of yet, and they can try,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1845}, {\"ngram\": \"insight\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"technique and different trick variations\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feed off their youth and their energy, because I just try to keep up.\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their youth\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"their energy\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am 50 years old and when they get all excited, 'Lets go, let us go, keep skating', I am 'yeah, I got to go and pick up the kids from school'.\\\"\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lets\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2126}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"the kids\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466 SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SITEMAP\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"MORE DOWNLOAD\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2247}, {\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2298}, {\"ngram\": \"Disinformation report hotline\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"010-85061466 SITEMAP\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2351}, {\"ngram\": \"OUR APP\